  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First, listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Why was the ambassador particularly lucky?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这位大使为什么格外幸运？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "When the ambassador of Escalopia returned home for lunch, his wife got a shock.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "埃斯卡洛皮亚大使回家吃午饭时，他的妻子吓了一跳。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "He looked pale, and his clothes were in a frightful state.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他脸色苍白，衣服也狼狈不堪。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "What has happened?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“发生什么事了？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "she asked.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她问道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "How did your clothes get into such a mess?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你的衣服怎么弄得这么乱？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "A fire extinguisher, my dear, answered the ambassador dryly.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“灭火器，亲爱的。”大使冷冷地回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "University students set the embassy on fire this morning.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“大学生今天上午放火烧了大使馆。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Good heavens!",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“天哪！”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "exclaimed his wife.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "妻子惊呼道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "And where were you at the time?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“当时你在哪里？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "I was in my office as usual, answered the ambassador.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我像往常一样在办公室里。”大使回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "The fire broke out in the basement.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“火是从地下室烧起来的。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "I went down immediately, of course, and that fool, Horst, aimed a fire extinguisher at me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我当然立刻下楼，那个叫霍斯特的傻瓜却拿灭火器对准了我。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "He thought I was on fire.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“他以为我身上着火了。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "I must definitely get that fellow posted.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我一定得把那家伙调走。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "The ambassador's wife went on asking questions when she suddenly noticed a big hole in her husband's hat.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "大使夫人继续追问，突然发现丈夫的帽子上有一个大洞。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "And how can you explain that?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“那这个你又怎么解释？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "she asked.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她问道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "Oh, that, said the ambassador.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“哦，那个啊，”大使说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "Someone fired a shot through my office window.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“有人朝我的办公室窗户开了一枪。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "Accurate, don't you think?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“枪法很准，你不觉得吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "text": "Fortunately, I wasn't wearing it at the time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“幸运的是，当时我没戴这顶帽子。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "text": "If I had been, I would not have been able to get home for lunch.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“如果戴着，我就没法回家吃午饭了。”"
      }
    }
  ],
